        <div class="answerLeft">
          <p class="til fz24" id="title">信鑫公告| 关于“清明”假期休市安排的通知</p>
          <p class="time"><em><i>2018-04-04 10:35:42&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;阅读465人</i></em>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;作者：信鑫资讯 </p>
          <div class="answerText">
            <div class="answerTextCont break">
              
            <div id="img-content" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;">
	<div class="rich_media_content " id="js_content" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;overflow:hidden;color:#3E3E3E;min-height:350px;position:relative;">
		<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;line-height:2em;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
			<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:2px;text-align:center;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;">尊敬的投资者：&nbsp;</span>
		</p>
		<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;line-height:2em;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
			<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:2px;text-align:center;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span>
		</p>
		<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;text-indent:37px;line-height:2em;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
			<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:2px;text-align:center;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;">您好！</span>
		</p>
		<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;text-indent:37px;line-height:2em;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
			<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:2px;text-align:center;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;">现将2018年清明假期休市安排公告如下：</span>
		</p>
		<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;text-indent:37px;line-height:2em;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
			<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:2px;text-align:center;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;">4月5日(星期四)至4月8日（星期日）休市，共4天。</span>
		</p>
		<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;text-indent:37px;line-height:2em;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
			<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:2px;text-align:center;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;">1、若您现持有期权合约到期日为4月5日或4月6日，则行权日期调整为4月9日。</span>
		</p>
		<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;text-indent:37px;line-height:2em;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
			<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:2px;text-align:center;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;">2、放假休市期间，我司官方网站、官方微信、可正常浏览，暂不进行信息更新。</span>
		</p>
		<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;text-indent:37px;line-height:2em;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
			<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:2px;text-align:center;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span>
		</p>
		<p style="text-align:left;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;text-indent:37px;line-height:2em;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
			<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:2px;text-align:center;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;">请您提前做好资金安排，对此给您带来的不便我们深表歉意。</span>
		</p>
		<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;text-indent:37px;text-align:justify;line-height:2em;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
			<br />
		</p>
		<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;text-indent:37px;text-align:center;line-height:2em;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
			<img data-src="https://res.wx.qq.com/mpres/htmledition/images/icon/common/emotion_panel/smiley/smiley_83.png" data-ratio="1" data-w="20" _width="20px" src="https://res.wx.qq.com/mpres/htmledition/images/icon/common/emotion_panel/smiley/smiley_83.png?wx_lazy=1" class="" data-fail="0" style="margin:0px;padding:0px;height:auto !important;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;display:inline-block;vertical-align:text-bottom;width:20px !important;visibility:visible !important;" />
		</p>
		<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;text-indent:37px;text-align:center;line-height:2em;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
			<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:2px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;">哦对了清明三天小长假</span>
		</p>
		<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;text-indent:37px;text-align:center;line-height:2em;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
			<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-size:14px;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:2px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;">高速公路假期实行免费通行政策</span></span>
		</p>
		<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;text-indent:37px;text-align:center;line-height:2em;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
			<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-size:14px;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:2px;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;">@股民 还是开着小车出去晒哈太阳呗</span></span>
		</p>
		<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;text-indent:37px;text-align:center;line-height:2em;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
			<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-size:14px;"></span>
		</p>
